#: addon\globalPlugins\LangDetectSpeech.py:212
msgid ""
"LangDetectSpeech requires \"Automatic language switching\" to be enabled in "
"NVDA speech settings.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to enable it now?"
msgstr ""
"LangDetectSpeech erfordert, dass \"Automatischer Sprachwechsel\" in den NVDA-"
"Spracheinstellungen aktiviert ist.\n"
"\n"
"Möchten Sie es jetzt aktivieren?"

#. Translators: Label for the languages section. {0} is the synthesizer name.
#: addon\globalPlugins\LangDetectSpeech.py:247
msgid ""
"Languages to detect\n"
"The synthesizer \"{0}\" supports the following languages. Select all that "
"should be considered for automatic detection:"
msgstr ""
"Zu erkennende Sprachen\n"
"Der Synthesizer \"{0}\" unterstützt die folgenden Sprachen. Wählen Sie alle "
"Sprachen aus, die für die automatische Erkennung berücksichtigt werden "
"sollen:"

#. Translators: Label for fallback language selection.
#. The description is included in the label so screen readers announce it.
#: addon\globalPlugins\LangDetectSpeech.py:263
msgid ""
"Fallback language\n"
"Used when the detected language is not in the list above:"
msgstr ""
"Ersatzsprache\n"
"Wird verwendet, wenn die erkannte Sprache nicht in der obigen Liste "
"enthalten ist:"

#. Add-on summary, usually the user visible name of the addon.
#. Translators: Summary for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in Add-ons Manager.
#: buildVars.py:23
msgid "LangDetectSpeech"
msgstr "Spracherkennung"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-ons manager
#: buildVars.py:26
msgid ""
"A lightweight NVDA addon that automatically detects the language of spoken "
"text and switches to the appropriate synthesizer voice. Uses fast-langdetect "
"(FastText-based) for efficient offline language detection across 176 "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Eine leichtgewichtige NVDA-Erweiterung, die automatisch die Sprache des "
"gesprochenen Textes erkennt und zur passenden Synthesizer-Stimme wechselt. "
"Verwendet fast-langdetect (FastText-basiert) für effiziente Offline-"
"Spracherkennung in 176 Sprachen."

